# Executive Summary

This meta-analysis investigates the performance and durability of Ionic Polymer-Metal Composites (IPMCs) with different electrode materials for load-bearing robotics applications.

**Research Question:** Do CNT-based electrodes demonstrate greater actuation displacement and longer durability under repeated load-bearing cycles compared to silver or copper electrodes?

