# 3. Data Preprocessing

```{r preprocess}
data <- data %>%
  mutate(
    electrode_group = factor(electrode_material),
    log_cycles = log(cycles_to_failure),
    env_aqueous = ifelse(environment == "Aqueous", 1, 0),
    calc_strain = ifelse(is.na(strain_percent), 
                         (displacement_mm / specimen_length_mm) * 100,
                         strain_percent)
  )
```

